reviewText: Scrubs will always be funny no matter how many times you watch it.
Love this show - still funny the second or 3rd times through.
I only received season 2 Scrubs. Season 1 Scrubs was not in the package.
Bought as a gift for boyfriend, loves this show. Dvds work good, I think it was the first season though the dvd case was cracked. Bought a new dvd case to replace.
I love scrubs and have all the seasons.  It is hard to turn off, and always makes me laugh. we watch it all the time
